message: Hi Bob, I'm offering you my product for $11,500.  It's a great deal, and I'm confident you'll find it very valuable. Let me know what you think!

I'm really interested in the product, but I was thinking more along the lines of $11,000. I've done some research and I think it's a bit overpriced at $11,500. I'd be willing to meet you halfway at $11,000.
